I thought on it long and hard.

1089
01:19:29,338 --> 01:19:31,298
It is melancholia.

1090
01:19:31,757 --> 01:19:33,342
Nothing more.

1091
01:19:34,510 --> 01:19:37,346
How can you fall into such despair?

1092
01:19:37,513 --> 01:19:40,474
How can you not know?

1093
01:19:42,560 --> 01:19:46,564
I ain't got no comfort in this life.

1094
01:19:48,816 --> 01:19:52,820
