1125
01:22:38,402 --> 01:22:40,696
Y'all bring no disrespect to me.

1126
01:22:40,821 --> 01:22:43,741
Don't bring no
biblical plagues to him, you hear?

1127
01:22:44,074 --> 01:22:46,160
Or I'll take it out on your skin.

1128
01:22:47,161 --> 01:22:48,496
Get out.

1129
