1203
01:29:41,426 --> 01:29:43,010
Not "Sir."

1204
01:29:43,761 --> 01:29:45,430
Just "Armsby."

1205
01:29:46,305 --> 01:29:48,433
I'm not owed
more than any other in the field.

1206
01:29:48,766 --> 01:29:51,769
How did you
arrive at such a place, if I may ask?

1207
01:29:52,103 --> 01:29:54,772
Ask, it's just conversation.

1208
01:29:56,816 --> 01:29:59,777
I became
a little too dependent on the whiskey...

1209
01:29:59,944 --> 01:30:02,321
a little too undependable on the job.

1210
01:30:03,740 --> 01:30:06,284
Now, before you say
I'm just a sorry drunkard...

1211
01:30:06,659 --> 01:30:08,745
let me state my case.

1212
01:30:09,704 --> 01:30:11,748
As reliable employment as overseeing is,

1213
01:30:11,914 --> 01:30:13,958
it is no easy chore on the spirit.

1214
01:30:14,834 --> 01:30:17,670
I say, no man of conscious...

1215
01:30:17,795 --> 01:30:20,173
can take the lash
to another human day in and day out...

1216
01:30:20,298 --> 01:30:22,842
without shredding at his own self.

1217
01:30:23,843 --> 01:30:25,970
Takes him to a place...

1218
01:30:26,095 --> 01:30:30,725
where he either makes
excuses within his mind to be unaffected...

1219
01:30:31,100 --> 01:30:34,395
or he finds some way
to trample his guilty sensations.

1220
01:30:35,313 --> 01:30:36,981
So, I trampled.

1221
01:30:37,106 --> 01:30:39,067
With frequency.

1222
01:30:40,693 --> 01:30:43,780
I gave in to tales of
wealth and prosperity.

1223
01:30:46,949 --> 01:30:51,412
But such profitable outcomes are
reserved for plantation masters.

1224
01:30:52,080 --> 01:30:55,249
It's the lot of the rest of us to serve.

1225
01:30:56,918 --> 01:31:02,256
Now, all I want is
to earn a decent wage and get myself home.

1226
01:31:23,111 --> 01:31:24,779
<i>(DOOR OPENING)</i>

1227
01:31:34,372 --> 01:31:36,666
The proceeds of
my fiddling performances.

1228
01:31:37,291 --> 01:31:41,421
Just a few picayunes,
but all I have in the world.

1229
01:31:42,088 --> 01:31:45,425
I promise them to you
if you will do me the favor I require.

1230
01:31:45,758 --> 01:31:49,846
