1234
01:31:56,853 --> 01:31:57,854
On my honor.

1235
01:31:59,939 --> 01:32:01,941
It's a simple enough request.

1236
01:32:03,276 --> 01:32:05,111
I only ask that you deposit a letter

1237
01:32:05,194 --> 01:32:06,988
at the post office in Marksville...

1238
01:32:07,113 --> 01:32:10,658
and that you keep the action
an inviolable secret forever.

1239
01:32:13,828 --> 01:32:16,164
A patron is what I require, Sir.

1240
01:32:22,837 --> 01:32:23,837
I'll do it.

1241
01:32:24,756 --> 01:32:27,133
And I'll accept whatever payment's offered.

1242
01:32:29,927 --> 01:32:32,388
To assist you, I put my own self at risk.

1243
01:32:33,181 --> 01:32:35,099
I will do so...

1244
01:32:35,224 --> 01:32:38,352
but fair compensation is all I ask.

1245
01:32:47,945 --> 01:32:49,947
Draw up your letter.

1246
01:32:50,114 --> 01:32:52,408
We'll meet again in two days?

1247
01:32:54,160 --> 01:32:56,037
In two days.

1248
01:32:58,831 --> 01:33:00,249
Thank you.

1249
